org.tensorflow.op.core

Class Zeros<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorflow.op.core.Zeros<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - constant type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Op, Operand<T>

    @Operator
public class Zeros<T>
extends Object
implements Op, Operand<T>
    An operator creating a constant initialized with zeros of the shape given by `dims`.

    For example, the following expression 

     ops.zeros(ops.constant(new long[]{2, 2}), Float.class)
    is the equivalent of 
    {@code ops.fill(ops.constant(new long[]{2, 2}), ops.constant(0.0f))
